sentences: Russ Narcies "Nar" Cabico (born September 16, 1990) is a Filipino singer, stage and TV actor known after being the grand champion of GMA Network's singing contest, Superstar Duets.
The last stage play he did was "3 Stars and a Sun", wherein he sang music from the late Francis Magalona.
In 2016, he became the first grand champion of the singing contest "Superstar Duets".
